Package zachary.shapes

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Circle
    This class represents a double precision circle, that draws a circle and can calculate basic properties of the circle, such as circumference and area
    Ellipse
    This class represents a double precision ellipse, that draws a ellipse and can calculate basic properties of the circle, such as circumference and area
    Line
    This class represents a double precision line, that draws a line and can calculate whether it intersects with another line
    Rectangle
    This class represents a double precision rectangle, that draws a rectangle and can calculate basic properties of the rectangle, such as finding the area or perimeter.
    RegularPolygon
    This class represents a double precision Polygon, that draws a polygon and can calculate basic math about it
    Shape
    This abstract class provides definitions for double precision geometric shapes.
    Shape2D
    This abstract class provides definitions for double precision geometric 2D shapes.
